sequenceDiagram
    participant C as Client
    participant P as API Port (FastAPI)
    participant S as Application Service
    participant R as Repository (Interface)
    participant A as Adapter (SQLAlchemy)
    participant DB as Database

    C->>P: HTTP Request
    P->>P: Validate (Pydantic)
    P->>S: Call service method
    S->>R: Repository call
    R->>A: Delegated to adapter
    A->>DB: SQL query
    DB-->>A: Result set
    A-->>R: Domain entity
    R-->>S: Domain entity
    S-->>P: DTO
    P-->>C: HTTP Response (JSON)
